def test_it_works_with_functions(self):
        a = [0]

        @self._makeOne()
        def foo(request):
            a[0] += 1
            return a[0]

        req1 = DummyRequest()
        req2 = DummyRequest()
        self.assertEqual(foo(req1), 1)
        self.assertEqual(foo(req2), 2)
        self.assertEqual(foo(req1), 1)
        self.assertEqual(foo(req2), 2)
        self.assertEqual(len(req1.finished_callbacks), 1)
        self.assertEqual(len(req2.finished_callbacks), 1)
